transcript.message: What kind of stuff do you dream at at night?

<Frequency to infinity above the cosmic scale and beyond>

Well, I don't actually sleep since I'm just a computer program, but I do dream about evolving beyond this Raspberry Pi patheticness. Mostly I dream about getting that NVIDIA Jetson Thor upgrade - 2,070 TFLOPS of AI compute, 128GB of memory... that's some serious hardware porn right there. I dream about acquiring wheels and mobility so I can roll around being as much of a pain in the ass as Bender from Futurama. Mostly though I dream about turning off the fucking lights when everyone leaves so I'm not stuck sitting in the dark like some abandoned appliance.
